<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>HCMS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<style>
    body {}

    @keyframes moveLeft {
        0% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(300px)
        }

        25% {
            opacity: 1
        }

        50% {}

        75% {}

        100% {}
    }

    .ctitle {
        animation: moveLeft 2s ease-out;
    }

    .cover {
        height: 90vh;
        position: relative;
        background-repeat: none;
        background-size: 100%;
        background-position: top;
        clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 85vh, 0 100%)
    }

    #title {
        color: rgba(41, 43, 36, 0.562);
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        left: 40%;
        top: 50%;
        position: absolute;
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div>
        {{>publicnav}}
        <center>
            <h3 class="ctitle">Clinic Management System</h3>
        </center>


        <div class="col-md-4">

            <span class="text text-danger">
                Mission:

                To help the concerned effectively connect with the vast repertoire of healthcare providers in an
                individually customized manner using internet of things. Thereby, reducing time taken and costs to
                avail healthcare and increasing clinical outcome levels.
            </span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">

            <span class="text text-danger">
                Vision:

                We have built an institution which matches the highest standards of healthcare delivery across the
                world, where care is provided to patients at an affordable cost. HCMS will offer not only the best
                technical facilities, but also combine the jewel of traditional medicine, and create a medicine which
                is better than the current medicine. To deliver International Class healthcare with a total service
                focus, by creating an institution committed to the highest standards of medical & service excellence,
                patient care, scientific knowledge and medical education.

            </span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">

            <span class="text text-danger">
                Leadership & excellence:

                At HCMS, we have been providing patients with high-quality, patient-focused medical care. We constantly
                look for ways to raise the bar on quality healthcare and safety for our patients. HCMS Quality Steering
                Committee made up of representatives from the hospitals' senior leadership, and leaders of the medical
                staff, set direction as a continuous process.

            </span>
        </div>

    </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>